# **1. Lane Executive Summary**

Lane 2 — Parser / Extraction / Evidence Automation has completed Blocks 1–3 on schedule. The parser framework is frozen, MBS and STAAD adapters are fully implemented with correct source priority tagging and confidence scoring, and evidence automation is 100% automated for all 5 core export tasks.

**Key Achievements:**
- BaseParser interface and FieldExtraction contract fully enforced
- MBS (P2) and STAAD (P1) adapters production-ready; no fallback pollution
- Evidence automation module generates compliant folder/file naming for BM-001 to BM-005
- All parser outputs are SQLite-write-ready pending two blocker clearances (B-PARSER-01, B-PARSER-02)

**Lane Status: AMBER** — Framework, adapters, and evidence foundation complete. Two external blockers prevent end-to-end testing. Block 5 (ETABS / Prota / PDF / Archive) is ready to proceed in parallel.

