**Key Contract Enforcements:**
- All 196 F-fields (F-001 to F-196) have mandatory field_id validation at construction
- No adapter can bypass hard confidence caps — enforced in FieldExtraction.__post_init__()
- Historical prohibition (P8) applies automatically regardless of adapter output
- write_to_db() stubbed with B-PARSER-01 / B-PARSER-02 guard — prevents premature writes

