### **Critical Confirmations (Block 2)**

- ✅ **SP-06 & SP-07 Bolt Handling:** Bolt fields absent → UNRESOLVED with zero confidence; no defaults inserted. Validated by T-PARSE-02 and T-PARSE-03.
- ✅ **MP-07 Built-up Section:** F-063 UNRESOLVED with FB-RULE-021 + BUILDUP_PLATE_REQUIRED flag when section name indicates composition (PL, PLATE, WELD, etc.). No inference of section type from geometry.
- ✅ **Fallback Govering Field Protection:** FieldExtraction.priority_rank + conflict_resolver enforcement prevents P7/P8 pollution. P8 Historical prohibition enforced at dataclass level.
- ✅ **Confidence Hard Caps:** Enforced at FieldExtraction.__post_init__(); adapters cannot inflate.

