# **3. Evidence Automation Progress**

## **3.1 Block 3 — Evidence Automation Foundation (COMPLETE)**

All 5 export tasks are **fully automated** in evidence_automation/evidence_exporter.py via single call to EvidenceExporter.export_all(benchmark_id).

| **Export Task** | **Implementation** | **Output** | **Status** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1. DB Snapshot | shutil.copy2() binary + conn.iterdump() SQL schema | .db + .sql | **AUTOMATED** |
| 2. Parser Log | SELECT * FROM project_file_registry (adapter, source, status, flags, timing) | .csv | **AUTOMATED** |
| 3. Extraction Log | SELECT * FROM field_extraction_log (immutable, all extractions + losers, chronological) | .csv | **AUTOMATED** |
| 4. field_value_store | SELECT * FROM field_value_store (winners only, CSV + JSON dual format) | .csv + .json | **AUTOMATED** |
| 5. Validation Result | SELECT * FROM validation_result (FB flags, UNRESOLVED, ESCALATE_IT, R-027 review) | .csv | **AUTOMATED** |
| 6. Evidence Manifest | JSON summary with benchmark_id, exported_at, artifact list | .json | **AUTOMATED** |

### **Guard: B-PARSER-02 DB Existence Check**

EvidenceExporter._check_db_exists() verifies SQLite DB exists before export begins. If DB-INIT-001 has not PASSED (tables missing), raises RuntimeError with explicit B-PARSER-02 reference — prevents silent empty evidence.

### **Folder & File Naming (Fully Compliant)**

**Evidence Folder Pattern:** {output_root}/{benchmark_id}_{YYYYMMDD}_{HHMMSS}/

**Benchmark Files Pattern:** {benchmark_id}_{artifact_type}_{YYYYMMDD}_{HHMMSS}.{ext}

Examples:
```
evidence/
  BM-001_20260427_143022/
    BM-001_db_snapshot_20260427_143022.db
    BM-001_db_schema_20260427_143022.sql
    BM-001_parser_log_20260427_143022.csv
    BM-001_extraction_log_20260427_143022.csv
    BM-001_field_value_store_20260427_143022.csv
    BM-001_field_value_store_20260427_143022.json
    BM-001_validation_result_20260427_143022.csv
    evidence_manifest.json
```

EvidenceFolderValidator confirms BM-001 to BM-005 compliance. Run timestamp captured once at EvidenceExporter construction and reused across all artifacts in single run.

