| **Adapter** | **Priority** | **Key Risk** | **Start Condition** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| ETABS Excel | P3 | >20% unmapped; openpyxl + pandas library handling | BaseParser frozen ✅; ODA (R-PARSER-01) optional |
