| PDF Image/OCR | P8 | Confidence cap 75%; PyMuPDF + Tesseract | BaseParser frozen ✅ |
| Archive (ZIP/RAR) | N/A | Encrypted files escalate to IT; zipfile + rarfile | BaseParser frozen ✅ |

**Block 5 Mandatory Tasks:**

1. Implement ETABS adapter (EP-01 through EP-10) — normalize Excel field extraction
2. Implement Prota DXF and PDF adapters (PP-01 through PP-08) — confirm geometry-only vs PDF fallback behavior
3. Implement PDF Text parser (P7) — confirm never-overrides rule
4. Implement PDF Image/OCR parser (P8) — apply 75% confidence cap; enforce HISTORICAL_PROHIBITED for governing fields
5. Implement Archive extractor — escalate encrypted files
6. Confirm DWG/DXF linkage and ODA integration
